.SH "Detailed Description"
.PP 
Handles image loading, GPU uploading, binding, and cleanup of texture resources\&. 

This class provides an abstraction over OpenGL texture operations\&. It supports 2D textures and wraps functionality for loading from file, uploading to GPU memory, and binding to specific texture units\&. 
